<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1150,1171]" pageId="14" pageNumber="85">Generic Name.</emphasis>
From Greek 
<emphasis box="[484,551,1151,1172]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="85">mythos</emphasis>
, meaning fable or legend and the generic name, 
<taxonomicName box="[175,232,1177,1198]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Apion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
